<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>taverna-fernando - Dashboard</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: sans-serif; padding: 20px; }
        .header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .logo { height: 60px; }
        .grid { display: flex; gap: 20px; }
        .card { border: 1px solid #ccc; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; width: 300px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Painel Administrativo - taverna-fernando</h1>
        <img src="https://www.tradework.com.br/media/catalog/product/cache/cd63a08b966d107aaaf66bd74393e948/r/e/red_hat_logo_big.jpg" alt="Logo" class="logo">
    </div>
    <div class="grid">
        <div class="card">
            <h3>Novo Item (Ingrediente)</h3>
            <form action="/add-item" method="POST">
                <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Nome (Ex: Batata Doce)" required><br><br>
                <input type="text" name="category" placeholder="Categoria (Ex: Carboidrato)"><br><br>
                <button type="submit">Cadastrar Item</button>
            </form>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h3>Itens Cadastrados</h3>
            <ul>
                <% items.forEach(item => { %>
                    <li><%= item.name %> (<%= item.category %>)</li>
                <% }) %>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <hr>
    <h2>📦 Pedidos Ativos</h2>
    <p><i>Aqui será implementado o Kanban nas próximas aulas...</i></p>
</body>
</html>
